        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "```{r}\n",
        "set.seed(STUDENT_ID)\n",
        "# Candidate 3: another manual candidate\n",
        "# fit_arima3 <- Arima(train_ts, order = c(p, d, q))\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "**Model comparison table:**\n",
        "\n",
        "| Model | Order (p,d,q) | AICc | In-sample RMSE |\n",
        "|-------|---------------|------|----------------|\n",
        "| ARIMA 1 | | | |\n",
        "| ARIMA 2 | | | |\n",
        "| ARIMA 3 | | | |\n",
        "\n",
        "**Model selection (2-3 sentences):** Which model do you select and why? How did you read the ACF/PACF to propose the candidate orders?\n",
        "\n",
        "## Seasonal ARIMA (10 pts)\n",
        "\n",
        "Extend to SARIMA(p,d,q)(P,D,Q)₂₄ with m=24 (hourly seasonality).\n",
