        "::: {.callout-tip}\n",
        "## Computation Note\n",
        "Seasonal ARIMA with m=24 can be very slow on long series. Use `stepwise=TRUE, approximation=TRUE` and consider limiting to the most recent training data. Fitting may take several minutes.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "```{r}\n",
